waypoints.name: This is a test for the longest waypoint name possible. I will keep going as long as it is unreasonable, as in theory, waypoints are stored in JSONB format and will not actually have a limit to how long their names can be, unlike Twist names which will also be tested during this entry. How long can I go? Who knows? I'll keep going on just a little longer now, but I have to admit I'm getting bored. Okay, let's end it here.

twists.name: Turner Street will be the test for the longest Twist name, which should be 255 characters. Let's see how far I can push this or if the database will be angry with me at some point. I'm counting all the characters and we should now be at 241. 246. 251. 255
